anc_ListItem.txt_Teaser: Unspoilt beaches, breathtaking natural beauty, unique wildlife and some of the world’s best cities, there’s certainly nothing like Australia.
Discover the freedom and thrill of the open road. Choose from 14 suggested itineraries for drives that capture the best sights and stops around Australia.
You don’t have to travel the globe to find the holiday of a lifetime. It’s all right here.
Using our expert knowledge and experience we’ll tailor the ideal holiday just for you. Because at House of Travel, we understand How Kiwis see the World.
With Air New Zealand we bring you more of Australia more often. Discover it for yourself -
Jetabout's services consist of everything you need to book the perfect holiday.
Experience Australia YOUR way. Your adventure starts at CheapTickets.sg. Book the cheapest flights, hotels & car hire online now at CheapTickets.sg
An Australian self drive with Chan Brothers Travel is one of the perfect ways to discover the breathtaking views, experience culture, heritage, wildlife and culinary delights.

SpecialOffersBox.txt_Accommodation: You’ll be spoilt for choice with Australian accommodation. We have boutique hotels and backpackers, luxury resorts and self-serviced apartments, rustic country pubs and camping.
SpecialOffersBox.txt_TravelAgentText: There are thousands of great Australian experiences to choose from. Chances are, your Aussie Specialist Travel Agent has experienced or planned for them before.

FeatureBoxItems.txt_Text: Explore these unique experiences to make your dream holiday come true.
Year-round outdoor adventure in 16 national parks and reserves.
A world of silent bushland and rich Aboriginal history.
Blue hazed beauty, eucalypt forests, caves, cliffs and waterfalls.
Beaches, surf culture, rainforest villages and spa indulgence.
A tapestry of wetlands, wildlife and Aboriginal rock art.
A place rich in Aboriginal culture and rugged outback beauty.
Four wheel drive beaches, rainforest and inland lakes.
Swim, dive, sail and island hop this ecological wonder.
A natural outback amphitheatre, opals and aboriginal rock art.
Meet Australia’s wildlife in pristine natural habitats.
Pink granite mountains, pristine beaches and turquoise sea.
Experience the beauty of Tasmania’s national parks.
Where tall forests, lakes and coastal wilderness connect.
Watch nature’s drama unfold around every turn.
Vast horizons, azure seas, gorges and natural wonders.
Australia's largest fringing reef offers amazing marine life.
